resent<ref name=\"CastroWin\">{{cite news |title=Angelina Castro Celebrates Her First AVN Award Win AVN |url=https://avn.com/business/press-release/video/angelina-castro-celebrates-first-ever-avn-award-for-favorite-bbw-762565.html |accessdate=14 January 2020 |work=AVN |date=2 February 2018 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321164119/https://avn.com/business/press-release/video/angelina-castro-celebrates-first-ever-avn-award-for-favorite-bbw-762565.html |archivedate=21 March 2019}}</ref>\n| known_for     = [[Big Beautiful Woman|BBW]] \n| children = 2<ref name=\"Cubano\">{{cite news |title=Angelina Castro: \u201cTener relaciones durante el embarazo es s\u00faper importante\u201d |url=https://www.periodicocubano.com/angelina-castro-tener-relaciones-durante-el-embarazo-es-super-importante/ |accessdate=14 January 2020 |work=PERI\u00d3DICO CUBANO |date=29 August 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200114065055/https://www.periodicocubano.com/angelina-castro-tener-relaciones-durante-el-embarazo-es-super-importante/ |archivedate=14 January 2020 |language=es}}</ref>\n| notable_works = \n|website= {{url|https://www.angelinacastrolive.com/}}\n}}\n'''Angelina Castro''' (born '''Francys Delia Valdez''' on 6 September 1982)<ref name=\"CubanHistory\"/> is a [[Cuban Americans|Cuban American]] [[pornographic actress]], film producer and radio personality. Castro grew up in Havana, Cuba, migrating to the United States when she was a child. After studying to be a chiropractor, Castro started working in [[porn|adult film]]s, starting in 2006, to pay off her student loans. The first Cuban-American adult film star, Castro gained national mainstream attention when she, and fellow porn actress Sara Jay, posted on [[Twitter]] that they would offer oral sex to fans of the [[Miami Heat]], if the Heat won the [[NBA Finals]] \u2013\u00a0and the two women did. Castro makes regular appearances on American Spanish-language radio and television, often providing sex advice, and is the spokesperson for Garner's Garden skincare.\n\n==Early life==\n\nAngelina Castro was born in 1982 in Havana, Cuba. She is a middle child, with a younger brother and an older sister.<ref name=\"CubanHistory\"/> When she was ten, her family moved to [[Santo Domingo]], [[Dominican Republic]]. Two years later, when she was twelve, the family relocated to Miami, Florida.<ref name=\"CubanHistory\"/><ref name=\"Urdaneta\">{{cite web |last1=Gonz\u00e1lez Urdaneta |first1=Luisana Mar\u00eda |title=La actriz porno cubana Angelina Castro cuenta su vida |url=https://cubanosporelmundo.com/2017/08/25/la-actriz-porno-cubana-angelina-castro-cuenta/ |website=Cubanos por el Mundo - Lo ultimo de Cuba y los cubanos |accessdate=14 January 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321163346/https://cubanosporelmundo.com/2017/08/25/la-actriz-porno-cubana-angelina-castro-cuenta/ |archivedate=21 March 2019 |language=es |date=25 August 2017}}</ref> Castro attended private schools in Miami.<ref name=\"CubanHistory\"/> As a teen, Castro participated in the [[1994 Cuban rafter crisis]] protests in Miami.<ref name=\"CubanHistory\"/> \n\n==Career==\n\nPrior to working in the adult film industry, Castro worked at [[Walgreens]] and as a stylist. She went to college to be a [[chiropractor]] and worked as a therapist.<ref name=\"CubanHistory\"/> Castro started in the pornographic industry in 2006. She began performing in adult films to pay off her student loans.<ref name=\"Biddle\"/>\n\nIn July 2012, during the [[NBA Finals]], Castro and fellow porn actress and promoter Sara Jay offered to perform [[oral sex]] on fans at a local nightclub in Miami if the [[Miami Heat]] won the championships. The Heat won, and Jay and Castro set up a website called \"TEAMBJNBA\" with the event information. The [[NBA]] filed a cease and desist letter and the website was taken down, however, the event still took place.<ref name=\"Mystal\">{{cite news |last1=Mystal |first1=Elie |title=Porn Stars Offer Free BJs to Miami Heat Fans, Cause NBA Lawyers To Stand At Attention |url=https://abovethelaw.com/2012/07/porn-stars-offer-free-bjs-to-miami-heat-fans-cause-nba-lawyers-to-stand-at-attention/ |accessdate=14 January 2020 |work=Above the Law |date=10 July 2012}}</ref><ref name=\"Munzenrieder\">{{cite news |last1=Munzenrieder |first1=Kyle |title=Local Porn Stars Will Make Good on Offer to Give Anyone a BJ After Heat Championship |url=https://www.miaminewtimes.com/news/local-porn-stars-will-make-good-on-offer-to-give-anyone-a-bj-after-heat-championship-6533481 |accessdate=14 January 2020 |work=Miami New Times |date=28 June 2012 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180705200008/https://www.miaminewtimes.com/news/local-porn-stars-will-make-good-on-offer-to-give-anyone-a-bj-after-heat-championship-6533481 |archivedate=5 July 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"Burns\">{{cite news |last1=Burns |first1=Ashley |title=Holy Crap, That Miami Heat Porn Star Oral Sex Celebration Actually Happened |url=https://uproxx.com/sports/holy-crap-that-miami-heat-porn-star-oral-sex-celebration-actually-happened/ |accessdate=14 January 2020 |work=UPROXX |date=13 August 2012 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191008181508/https://uproxx.com/sports/holy-crap-that-miami-heat-porn-star-oral-sex-celebration-actually-happened/ |archivedate=8 October 2019}}</ref> Castro was interviewed on [[Radio Marti]]'s 1800 Online in September 2012. Castro's interview, which included how she entered the porn industry and how Cubans could get involved in the porn industry, was removed from the radio show's website after public backlash.<ref name=\"Biddle\"/> In 2015, Castro began co-hosting ''SOS'' (Sex or Sexy) on Mira.tv in Florida, a radio show focused on sex and sexuality in the [[Latinx]] community.<ref name=\"Cubano\"/><ref name=\"Johnson\">{{cite news |last1=Johnson |first1=Bob |title=Angelina Castro Hosts New Mainstream Spanish Sex TV Show |url=https://www.xbiz.com/news/196172/angelina-castro-hosts-new-mainstream-spanish-sex-tv-show |accessdate=14 January 2020 |work=XBIZ |date=26 June 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180303155722/http://www.xbiz.com/news/196172/angelina-castro-hosts-new-mainstream-spanish-sex-tv-show |archivedate=3 March 2018 |language=en}}</ref> \n\nDuring the [[2016 United States presidential election]], Castro and Maggie Green, also a porn actress, made national news when they offered to give [[blow job]]s to voters, who voted for Hillary Clinton, if Clinton won the election.<ref name=\"Powell\">{{cite web |last1=Powell |first1=Austin |title=Porn Stars Angelina Castro and Maggie Green Offer Blowjobs to Everyone Who Votes Against Trump |url=https://www.dailydot.com/irl/porn-stars-blowjob-donald-trump/ |website=The Daily Dot |accessdate=14 January 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191121184000/https://www.dailydot.com/irl/porn-stars-blowjob-donald-trump/ |archivedate=21 November 2019 |language=en |date=7 November 2016}}</ref> In 2018, Castro won her first [[AVN Award]] for [[Big Beautiful Woman|BBW]] Performer of the Year.<ref name=\"rolandAVN\">{{cite news |last1=Roland |first1=John |title=2018 AVN Award Winners Announced AVN |url=https://avn.com/business/articles/video/2018-avn-award-winners-announced-759869.html |accessdate=14 January 2020 |work=AVN |date=3 September 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903113036/https://avn.com/business/articles/video/2018-avn-award-winners-announced-759869.html |archivedate=3 September 2019}}</ref> Castro appeared on the Puerto Rican television program ''[[Esto no tiene nombre (tv show)|Esto no tiene nombre]]'' in August 2019, during which she gave tips on how to have sex while pregnant.<ref name=\"Cubano\"/> In 2019, she also became a spokesperson for the natural skin care company, Garner's Garden.<ref name=\"Garners\">{{cite web |title=Angelina Castro Is The New Brand Ambassador For Garner's Garden AVN |url=https://avn.com/business/press-release/novelty/angelina-castro-new-brand-ambassador-for-skin-care-line-812532.html |website=AVN |accessdate=14 January 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190116002558/https://avn.com/business/press-release/novelty/angelina-castro-new-brand-ambassador-for-skin-care-line-812532.html |archivedate=16 January 2019 |date=15 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Personal life==\n\nCastro lives in Miami, Florida. She has two children.<ref name=\"Cubano\"/>\n\n== Awards ==\n*2018 &mdash; [[AVN Award]] &mdash; BBW Performer of the Year<ref name=\"rolandAVN\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{official|https://www.angelinacastrolive.com/}}\n*{{IMDb name|4230393|Angelina Castro}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Castro, Angelina}}\n[[Category:1982 births]]\n[[Category:American pornographic film actresses]]\n[[Category:Hispanic and Latino American pornographic film actors]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Cuban businesspeople]]\n[[Category:Actresses from Havana]]\n[[Category:Actresses from Miami]]\n[[Category:21st-century American actresses]]\n[[Category:21st-century American businesswomen]]\n[[Category:21st-century American businesspeople]]\n[[Category:American pornographic film producers]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Cuban-American pornographic actress}}\n\n{{Infobox person\n| name          = Angelina Castro\n| image         = Angelina Castro AVN Adult Entertainment Expo 2013.jpg \n|alt           = \n| caption       = Angelina Castro in 2013\n| birth_name    = Francys Delia Valdes<ref name=\"CubanHistory\">{{cite web |title=ANGELINA CASTRO, Actress and Model. (Born: Santiago de Cuba.) + ANGELINA CASTRO, Actress y Modelo. (Nacida en Santiago de Cuba). {{!}} The History, Culture and Legacy of the People of Cuba |url=https://www.thecubanhistory.com/2016/01/angelina-castro-actress-and-model-born-havana-angelina-castro-actress-y-modelo-nacida-en-la-habana/ |website=The Cuban History |accessdate=14 January 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104052644/http://www.thecubanhistory