)|507th Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army JRTC Flash.png|<center>[[Fort Polk|Joint Readiness Training Center]] (JRTC)-Army Element</center>\nFile:US Army 1st Bn-509th Inf Reg Flash.png|<center>JRTC's [[509th Infantry Regiment (United States)|509th Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army JROTC Flash.png|<center>[[Junior Reserve Officers' Training Corps]]</center>\nFile:US Army C Company, 262nd Quartermaster Battalion Flash.png|<center>[[Quartermaster Center and School]]'s 262nd Quartermaster Battalion</center>\nFile:Security Force Assistance Command Flash.svg|<center>[[Security Force Assistance Command]] (SFAC)</center>\nFile:1st Security Force Assistance Brigade Flash.svg|<center>SFAC's [[1st Security Force Assistance Brigade]]</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd Security Force Assistance Brigade Flash.svg|<center>SFAC's [[2nd Security Force Assistance Brigade]]</center>\nFile:US Army 3rd Security Force Assistance Brigade Flash.svg|<center>SFAC's [[3rd Security Force Assistance Brigade]]</center>\nFile:US Army 4th Security Force Assistance Brigade Beret Flash.svg|<center>SFAC's 4th Security Force Assistance Brigade</center>\nFile:US Army 5th Security Force Assistance Brigade Beret Flash.svg|<center>SFAC's 5th Security Force Assistance Brigade</center>\nFile:US Army 54th Security Force Assistance Brigade Beret Flash.svg|<center>SFAC's 54th Security Force Assistance Brigade</center>\nFile:USAJFKSWCS flash.gif|<center>[[John F. Kennedy Special Warfare Center and School|US Army John F. Kennedy Special Warfare Center and School]] (SWCS)</center>\nFile:US Army Special Forces Warrant Officer Institute Flash.png|<center>SWCS's Special Forces Warrant Officer Institute</center>\nFile:US Army Special Warfare Education Group Flash.png|<center>SWCS's Special Warfare Education Group</center>\nFile:US Army Special Warfare Medical Group Flash.png|<center>SWCS's Special Warfare Medical Group</center>\nFile:US Army Special Warfare NCO Academy Flash.png|<center>SWCS's Special Warfare [[Non-Commissioned Officer]] Academy</center>\nFile:US Army Special Warfare Training Group Flash.png|<center>SWCS's 1st Special Warfare Training Group</center>\nFile:US Army 18th Airborne Corps NCO Academy Flash.png|<center>[[XVIII Airborne Corps]]'s [[Enlisted Professional Military Education|Non-Commissioned Officer Academy]]</center>\nFile:US Army Advanced Airborne School Flash.png|<center>[[82nd Airborne Division]]'s [[United States Army Jumpmaster School|Advanced Airborne School]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n===US Air Force===\n<gallery>\nFile:USAF Combat Aviation Advisor flash.svg|<center>Combat Aviation Advisor ([[6th Special Operations Squadron]] (SOS) and [[711th Special Operations Squadron|711th SOS]])</center>\nFile:USAF Combat Controller Flash.jpg|<center>[[United States Air Force Combat Control Team|Combat Controller]]</center>\nFile:USAF Combat Rescue Officer Flash.png|<center>[[Combat rescue officer|Combat Rescue Officer]]</center>\nFile:USAF Pararescue Flash.jpg|<center>[[Pararescueman]]</center>\nFile:USAF Security Forces beret flash.jpg|<center>[[United States Air Force Security Forces|Security Forces]]</center>\nFile:USAF Security Forces flash-Officer.png|<center>Security Forces Officer</center>\nFile:USAF Special Reconnaissance Flash.png|<center>[[United States Air Force Special Reconnaissance|Special Reconnaissance]]</center>\nFile:USAF Special Tactics Officer Flash.png|<center>[[United States Air Force Special Tactics Officer|Special Tactics Officer]]</center>\nFile:USAF SERE Flash.jpg|<center>[[Survival, Evasion, Resistance and Escape]] Instructor</center>\nFile:USAF Tactical Air Control Party Beret Flash.svg|<center>[[United States Air Force Tactical Air Control Party|Tactical Air Control Party]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n==See also==\n* [[Obsolete badges of the United States military]]\n* [[Badges of the United States Air Force]]\n* [[Uniforms of the United States Air Force]]\n* [[Uniforms of the United States Navy]