 /> and [[YouPorn]].<ref name=\"auto\"/><ref name=\"MindGeek Settles Cybersquatting Suits\" />\n\nThe three highest ranking sites in the Pornhub Network are Pornhub, RedTube and YouPorn. In November 2013, it was reported that Pornhub has over 1&nbsp;billion visitors per month,<ref name=\"World's biggest porn site news.com.au Pornhub\">{{cite web|title=World's biggest porn site reveals how major events affect viewing habits|url=http://www.news.com.au/technology/online/worlds-biggest-porn-site-reveals-how-major-events-affect-viewing-habits/story-fnjwmwrh-1226770342473|website=news.com.au|accessdate=22 December 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019085947/http://www.news.com.au/technology/online/worlds-biggest-porn-site-reveals-how-major-events-affect-viewing-habits/story-fnjwmwrh-1226770342473|archivedate=19 October 2014|date=28 November 2013}}</ref> and a December 2014 article in ''[[Adweek]]'' states that Pornhub has 50 million daily visitors.<ref name=\"Inside Pornhub's Crusade, Adweek\">{{cite web|last1=Monllos|first1=Kristina|title=Inside Pornhub's Crusade to Tear Down the Taboos of Watching Sex Online|url=http://www.adweek.com/news/advertising-branding/inside-pornhubs-crusade-tear-down-taboos-watching-sex-online-161910|website=Adweek|accessdate=22 December 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219032754/http://www.adweek.com/news/advertising-branding/inside-pornhubs-crusade-tear-down-taboos-watching-sex-online-161910|archivedate=19 December 2014|date=18 December 2014}}</ref> Pornhub.com scores at [[Alexa Internet|Alexa Global Rank]] 27 (as of 18 March 2019).<ref name=\"Alexa pornhub.com Site Overview March 18, 2019\">{{cite web|title=pornhub.com Site Overview |url=http://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/pornhub.com |website=Alexa |accessdate=18 March 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190318172042/https://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/pornhub.com |archivedate=18 March 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\nTrafficEstimate.com said that Redtube.com