{"title_page": "Abella Danger", "text_new": "{{short description|pornographic actress}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=October 2019}}\n{{unreliable sources|date=October 2019}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Abella Danger \n| image              = Abella Danger Tux 2017.jpg\n| caption            = Danger at the AVN Awards Show in [[Las Vegas, Nevada]], January 2017\n| birth_date         = {{nowrap|{{birth date and age|mf=yes|1995|11|19}}}}<ref name=IAFD>{{iafd name|id=abelladanger|gender=female|name=Abella Danger}}</ref>\n| birth_place        = [[Miami]], [[Florida]], U.S.<ref name=IAFD />\n| height             = 5 ft 6 in<ref name=IAFD />\n| weight             = 130 lb<ref name=IAFD />\n| partner            = Gaby G \n| alias              = Bella Danger<ref name=IAFD />\n| years_active       = 2014\u2013present<ref name=IAFD/>\n| website            =\n}}\n\n'''Abella Danger''' (born November 19, 1995) is an American [[Pornographic film actor|pornographic actress]] and [[Model (person)|model]].<ref name=IAFD /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/brazzers-wants-to-save-the-bees-with-what-else-bee-porn/|title=Pornhub Wants to Save the Bees With (What Else?) Bee Porn|last=Cohen|first=David|date=April 19, 2019|website=Adweek|language=en-US|access-date=May 26, 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\n[[File:Abella Danger 2016.jpg|thumb|upright|Abella Danger in 2016]]\nDanger made her [[Pornographic film|adult film]] debut in July 2014 for [[Bang Bros]].<ref name=AEENewbie>{{cite magazine|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/video/AEE-Newbie-Abella-Danger-Miami-Heat-Hits-L-A-584189.html |title=AEE Newbie: Abella Danger, Miami Heat Hits L.A.|accessdate=January 16, 2016|author=Peter Warren|date=January 21, 2015|magazine=[[AVN (magazine)|AVN]]}}</ref> She moved from [[Miami]], Florida to [[Los Angeles]], California after filming eight scenes.<ref name=AEENewbie /> She was the Twisty's Treat of the Month in July 2016.<ref>{{cite web|title=Twistys treats and treat of the month index|url=https://www.lemmecheck.com/twistys-totm-index/ |website=lemmecheck.com}}</ref> She has attended the [[AVN Adult Entertainment Expo]]. According to the IAFD website, she has appeared in approximately 936 credited scenes with 62 of those being duplicate scenes in compilations.<ref name=IAFD/> This includes streaming and DVD.<ref name=IAFD/>  She has appeared in mainstream news media other than adult news media, including the websites ''[[Elite Daily]]''<ref>[https://www.elitedaily.com/dating/sex/adult-film-star-on-set-stories/1826731 Porn Stars Get Real About Their Most Cringeworthy Stories<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>\u00a0and ''International Business Times''.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Pressberg |first1=Matt |title=How Virtual Reality Is Bringing Acting Back To The Porn Industry |url=https://www.ibtimes.com/how-virtual-reality-bringing-acting-back-porn-industry-2357887 |accessdate=31 March 2020 |work=International Business Times |date=24 April 2016}}</ref> ''[[Fortune (magazine)|Fortune]]'', in 2018, acknowledged her as one of the most popular and in-demand performers in the business.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Morris |first1=Chris |title=Call 'Em the Dirty Dozen: The 12 Most Popular Stars in Adult Entertainment |url=https://fortune.com/2018/01/24/most-popular-adult-film-stars/ |accessdate=11 January 2020 |work=Fortune |date=2018-01-24 |language=en}}</ref> \n\nIn 2019, Danger was cast in ''Her and Him'', the directorial debut of [[Bella Thorne]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2481536/bella-thorne-reveals-why-she-decided-to-create-a-porn-movie|title=Bella Thorne reveals why she decided to create a porn movie|work=Cinema Blend}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.papermag.com/bella-thorne-pornhub-2639806202.html|title=Bella Thorne Directed a Film For Pornhub|last=Goldfine|first=Jael|date=August 13, 2019|website=[[Paper (magazine)|Paper]]|language=en|url-status=live|access-date=October 13, 2019}}</ref> The short film is produced by [[Pornhub]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://toofab.com/2019/08/27/bella-thorne-mod-sun-split-tana-mongeau-directing-pornhub-movie/|title=Bella Thorne Spills on Mod Sun Split, Tana Mongeau, Directing Pornhub Movie|date=August 27, 2019|website=toofab|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009093803/https://toofab.com/2019/08/27/bella-thorne-mod-sun-split-tana-mongeau-directing-pornhub-movie/|archive-date=October 9, 2019|access-date=September 28, 2019}}</ref> and is the third film in the company's Visionaries Director's Club series. Danger also features in the second film in the series, ''I Love You''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newsweek.com/former-disney-star-bella-thorne-makes-her-directorial-debut-her-him-pornhub-1454177|title=Former Disney star Bella Thorne makes her directorial debut with \"Her & Him\" for Pornhub|last=Keeley|first=Matt|date=August 13, 2019|website=Newsweek|language=en-US|url-status=live|access-date=October 13, 2019}}</ref>\n\nDanger contributed vocals and appears in the music video to the song, 911, by [[Borgore]] off his album, ''The Art of Gore''.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Cameron |first1=John |title=6 Adult Film Stars Who Happen to be Diehard Fans of EDM |url=https://edm.com/features/6-adult-film-stars-diehard-fans-edm |accessdate=11 January 2020 |work=EDM.com - The Latest Electronic Dance Music News, Reviews & Artists |date=2019-10-09 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Sani |first1=Niko |title=Borgore Drops Music Video for \"911\" ft. Abella Danger on Pornhub |url=https://edm.com/music-releases/borgore-abella-danger-911 |accessdate=11 January 2020 |work=EDM.com - The Latest Electronic Dance Music News, Reviews & Artists |date=2019-07-20 |language=en}}</ref>\n\n== Personal life ==\nDanger was raised in a [[Jewish]] household and was a ballet dancer while growing up.<ref>{{cite interview|subject=Abella Danger|interviewer= |title=Interview with Best New Starlet Abella Danger|url=https://www.hotmovies.com//interviews/abella-danger-interview?spotlight=interviews&permalink=abella-danger-interview |publisher=HotMovies|location= |date= |archiveurl= |archivedate= }}</ref><ref name=\":0\">{{cite interview|subject=Abella Danger|interviewer=Captain Jack|title=Abella Danger: All Access|url=https://interviews.adultdvdtalk.com/abella-danger/ |publisher=Adult DVD Talk|location= |date=March 25, 2015|archiveurl= |archivedate= }}</ref> She has been trained in classical dancing.<ref name=\":0\" /> Danger chose her stage name, \"Abella\" from the derivative Bella, which means beautiful in Italian.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fleshlight.com/products/abella-danger|title=Abella Danger|last1=Danger|first1=Abella|website=fleshlight}}</ref>\n\nDanger is in a relationship with Gaby Guerrero (Gaby G) and appears in her music video, \"City on Fire\". She plays a character luring the singer to the dark side of Los Angeles.<ref>{{cite news |title=Los Angeles is a \u201cCity on Fire\u201d in Gaby G\u2019s new video |url=https://earmilk.com/2019/04/15/los-angeles-is-a-city-on-fire-in-gaby-gs-new-video/ |accessdate=11 January 2020 |work=EARMILK |date=15 April 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Jerome |first1=Cristina |title=As Miami Beach Pride Nears, Native Youth Opens Up About Her Sexuality |url=https://www.miaminewtimes.com/music/native-youth-opens-up-about-her-sexuality-before-miami-beach-gay-pride-10214108 |accessdate=11 January 2020 |work=Miami New Times |date=6 April 2018}}</ref>\n\n== Awards ==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ [[AVN Award]]s\n|-\n! Year\n! Result\n! Award\n! Film\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\"| 2016<ref>{{cite web|last1=Machado|first1=Sam|title=AVN Award Winners 2016: See Who Won In Porn At The Raciest Ceremony In Entertainment|url=http://www.enstarz.com/articles/137645/20160124/avn-award-winners-2016-see-who-won-in-porn-at-the-raciest-ceremony-in-entertainment.htm |website=Enstars.com|accessdate=January 24, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://business.avn.com