s a [[Hungarian people|Hungarian]]-[[Norwegian people|Norwegian]] actor and director. As a young man, he moved to Norway as a Hungarian refugee, eventually moving to the United States to pursue a career as a pilot, which eventually led to a career in film. While he acted in mainstream films, he was a [[look-alike]]  for [[Burt Reynolds]] and [[Sean Connery]], which popularized him in adult films, including parodies. He started making porn at age 38 and retired in his sixties, with over 500 films<ref name=\"Haga\">{{cite news |last1=Haga |first1=Sverre Gunnar |title=Sasha vil lage norsk porno |url=https://www.dagbladet.no/kultur/sasha-vil-lage-norsk-porno/65698611 |accessdate=18 January 2020 |work=[[Dagbladet]] |date=15 March 2001 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200118055815/https://www.dagbladet.no/kultur/sasha-vil-lage-norsk-porno/65698611 |archivedate=18 January 2020 |language=no}}</ref> in his canon. Described as a [[wikt:provocateur|provocateur]] and Norway's most famous porn actor by ''[[Morgenbladet]]'', the thrice-married Gabor was a womanizing alcoholic who played accordion, spoke eight languages, and was one of [[Ron Jeremy]]'s best friends.<ref name=\"Hunter\"/><ref name=\"Pornokongen\"/> \n\n==Early life==\n\nGabor Sark\u00f8zy<ref name=\"VGObit\"/> was born in 1945 in [[Hungary]]. He moved to [[Lillestr\u00f8m]], [[Norway]] in 1957 as a refugee in the wake of the [[Hungarian_Revolution_of_1956#Hungary|Hungarian Revolution]].<ref name=\"Hunter\"/> He left school and he played [[accordion]], trumpet, and double bass for [[Cirkus Arnardo]].<ref name=\"Romerikes\">{{cite web |title=Pornostjerne fra Lillestr\u00f8m funnet d\u00f8d |url=https://www.rb.no/lokale-nyheter/pornostjerne-fra-lillestrom-funnet-dod/s/1-95-3660400 |publisher=[[Romerikes Blad]] |accessdate=18 January 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305081115/http://www.rb.no/lokale-nyheter/pornostjerne-fra-lillestrom-funnet-dod/s/1-95-3660400 |archivedate=5 March 2016 |language=no |date=10 July 2008}}</ref> He eventually moved to the United States, where he joined the [[United States Army]] and went to school to become an airplane pilot.<ref name=\"Romerikes\"/>\n\n==Career==\nPrior to acting, Gabor worked as a commercial airline pilot. Gabor eventually lost his commercial pilot license due to alcohol-related arrests.<ref name=\"Warren\"/> \n\nIn the early 1980s, Gabor was acting in small parts in mainstream films in Los Angeles. He was a [[Burt Reynolds]] [[lookalike]], which he capitalized on, including working as a stand in for Reynolds in films. In 1982, Gabor met [[Ron Jeremy]] while filming the [[Jerry Lewis]] comedy ''[[Cracking Up (film)|Cracking Up]]''.<ref name=\"Warren\">{{cite news |last1=Warren |first1=Peter |title=Ron Jeremy Remembers Sasha Gabor AVN |url=https://avn.com/business/articles/video/ron-jeremy-remembers-sasha-gabor-53677.html |accessdate=18 January 2020 |work=AVN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190711063951/https://avn.com/business/articles/video/ron-jeremy-remembers-sasha-gabor-53677.html |archivedate=10 July 2008}}</ref> Gabor and Jeremy saw each other again at an [[Adult Film Association of America]] gala in 1983. Attendees usually dressed in costumes and Gabor did his Burt Reynolds [[shtick]] including arriving in a black sports car complete with a vanity license plate reading \"[[Smokey and the Bandit|Bandit]]\".<ref name=\"Warren\"/> Gabor told Jeremy he was interested in the [[porn]] industry and Jeremy introduced Gabor to his adult film industry contacts. He was 38 when he made his first adult film.<ref name=\"Hunter\"/>\n\nGabor acted regularly in films by Bobby Bouchard. He performed in Burt Reynolds parody porn films, using the stage name '''Turd Wrenolds'''. He co-starred in the ''[[Smokey and the Bandit]]'' parody ''All-American Girls in Heat''.<ref name=\"Warren\"/><ref name=\"Stenerud\">{{cite web |last1=Stenerud |first1=David |title=Pornoen stjeler stjernene |url=https://www.seher.no/kjendis/pornoen-stjeler-stjernene/64920637 |website=Se og H\u00f8r |accessdate=18 January 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929023812/http://www.seher.no/kjendis/pornoen-stjeler-stjernene-16262 |archivedate=29 September 2015 |language=no |date=10 August 2007}}</ref> Gabor also had [[plastic surgery]] to appear more like Reynolds.<ref name=\"Warren\"/>\n\nGabor was also a regular in Jeremy's films in the late 1980s, when Jeremy was a director for Leisure Time Entertainment. They filmed many films together, including 20 to 30 films on [[houseboat]]s at [[Lake Mead]] with Samantha Strong and [[Tracey Adams]], the result of having to film out of state due to [[obscenity]] laws in Los Angeles.<ref name=\"Hunter\"/> Gabor's alcohol abuse often impacted his ability to get an [[erection]], and Jeremy would often stand in for Gabor. Jeremy estimated that one-third of Gabor's films showed Jeremy's circumcised penis in lieu of Gabors uncircumcised penis. Jeremy would serve as one of Gabor's bestfriends throughout Gabor's life.<ref name=\"Warren\"/>\n\nHe traveled frequently to [[Thailand]], where he'd vacation and also get plastic surgery, which he documented in photographs. Gabor stopped dying his hair black and let it go gray and got plastic surgery to look more like [[Sean Connery]]. Back in the United States, he worked as a Connery lookalike outside of porn, attending special events. Gabor lived in [[Marina del Rey, California]] followed by [[Tampa, Florida]].<ref name=\"Warren\"/>\n\nHe retired from acting in 2001 and moved back to Norway after too many alcohol-related arrests and to escape from paying [[child support]].<ref name=\"Hunter\"/><ref name=\"Warren\"/> In Norway, Gabor planned to direct the first Norwegian professional porn film.<ref name=\"Haga\"/> In 2007, Gabor said he was going to direct a [[S\u00e1mi people|S\u00e1mi]]-themed adult film in [[Kautokeino]], Norway. The film was never made.<ref name=\"MoHanssen\">{{cite news |last1=Mo Hanssen |first1=Anders |title=Pornostjerne vil lage sameporno i Finnmark |url=https://www.nordlys.no/nyheter/pornostjerne-vil-lage-sameporno-i-finnmark/s/1-79-2501535 |accessdate=18 January 2020 |work=www.nordlys.no |date=4 January 2007 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055038/http://www.nordlys.no/nyheter/pornostjerne-vil-lage-sameporno-i-finnmark/s/1-79-2501535 |archivedate=4 March 2016 |language=no}}</ref><ref name=\"Lundh\">{{cite news |last1=Lundh |first1=Francis |title=Sasha Gabor klar for same-porno |url=https://www.vg.no/rampelys/i/b365B/sasha-gabor-klar-for-same-porno |accessdate=18 January 2020 |work=[[Verdens Gang]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090723/http://www.vg.no/rampelys/sasha-gabor-klar-for-same-porno/a/163665/ |archivedate=4 March 2016 |language=nb}}</ref>\n\n===Views on the film industry===\n\nGabor believed pornographic films were beneficial for men and women to watch, suggesting one can learn that \"there is no one way to make girls [[orgasm|climax]]\" and that one can \"learn many things from porn movies.\"<ref name=\"Haga\"/>\n\n==Later life and legacy==\n\nGabor was an [[alcoholic]], which Ron Jeremy called \"the bane of [Gabor's] existence.\"<ref name=\"Warren\"/> Gabor had been arrested for [[driving under the influence]] multiple times, having his license suspended indefinately.<ref name=\"VGObit\"/><ref name=\"South\">{{cite web |title=Sasha Gabor Found Dead in Thailand |url=http://mikesouth.com/porn-deaths/sasha-gabor-found-dead-in-thailand-2206/ |website=Mike South |accessdate=18 January 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520232718/http://mikesouth.com/porn-deaths/sasha-gabor-found-dead-in-thailand-2206/ |archivedate=10 July 2008 |date=10 July 2008}}</ref> \n\nAfter retiring in 2001, Gabor moved back to Norway.<ref name=\"Hunter\"/> Norwegian journalist [[Alex Ros\u00e9n]] featured Gabor in his documentary series ''People on the Move'' for [[NRK1]]. The film was supposed to be aired in February 2001, but was delayed until March due to the controversial nature of the program. The film featured Gabor participating in a [[gang bang]].<ref name=\"NRK1\">{{cite news |title=NRK viser porno-dokumentar |url=https://www.bt.no/kultur/i/8pVM2/NRK-viser-porno-dokumentar |accessdate=18 January 2020 |work=[[Bergens Tidende]] |date=9 March 2001 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200118063216/https://www.bt.no/kultur/i/8pVM2/NRK-viser-porno-dokumentar |archivedate=18 January 2020 |language=nb}}</ref>\nGabor died of [[cardiac arrest]] on 27 June 2008 on vacation in [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]].<ref name=\"Haga\"/><ref name=\"Golf\">{{cite web |last1=Golf |first1=Silje Julie |title=D\u00f8de p\u00e5 ferie i Thailand |url=http://www.klikk.no/produkthjemmesider/herogna/nyheter/dode-pa-ferie-i-thailand-3089239 |publisher=Klikk |accessdate=18 January 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009062524/http://www.klikk.no/produkthjemmesider/herogna/nyheter/dode-pa-ferie-i-thailand-3089239 |archivedate=9 October 2017 |language=no |date=9 October 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"Johnsen\">{{cite web |last1=Johnsen |first1=Vibeke |title=Sasha Gabor er d\u00f8d |url=https://www.nettavisen.no/nyheter/sasha-gabor-er-dod/2061248.html |publisher=Nettavisen |accessdate=18 January 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081617/http://www.nettavisen.no/nyheter/sasha-gabor-er-dd/2061248.html |archivedate=10 July 2008 |language=no |date=10 July 2008}}</ref> Gabor was married three times and had five children.<ref name=\"Romerikes\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons cat}}\n* {{IMDb name|0300139|Sasha Gabor}}\n* {{iafd name|id=sgabor|gender=male|name=Sasha Gabor}}\n* {{afdb name|id=1594|gender=male|name=Sasha Gabor}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Gabor, Sasha}}\n[[Category:1945 births]]\n[[Category:2008 deaths]]\n[[Category:Hungarian refugees]]\n[[Category:Refugees in Norway]]\n[[Category:Hungarian emigrants to Norway]]\n[[Category:Hun